description: Eastwood Schools is a collection of K-12 private IB World schools that utilize tech-enabled learning methodologies to modernize education and improve engagement in Lebanon and the region.
EasyUni is an online university search portal that aggregates information for prospective students to compare and choose courses and facilitate an end-to-end application process.
EAT Restaurant Group owns and operates 43 restaurants under 9 distinct brands globally. In 2019, EAT also introduced 3 virtual brands through cloud-based kitchens.
Ebizmarts provides retailers with Point-of-Sale software and related app to connect any of their physical and online stores, enabling them to sell more and be more profitable.
Eco-Lógica provides an end-to-end corporate waste management solution that allows clients to dispose of waste safely and efficiently, while helping them comply with environmental policies.
Ecocoast specializes in engineering, manufacturing, and installing sustainable solutions for companies in the marine industry.
Ecomobi is a social selling platform that connects influencers/content creators to brands and e-commerce merchants, enabling them to sell and advertise their products directly to customers.
Econduce is a sustainable urban transportation company that runs a network of shared electric scooters.
Ecopacific is Ecuador’s leading juice company which vertically integrates its processes and develops an end-to-end value chain.

EcoSystems is a leading provider of water and energy conservation services in the US. The company designs and implements savings programs, including Freddie/Fannie green loan program, for the multifamily apartment, hotel, nursing home and condominium industries.

EDJ Analytics develops customized algorithms for clients who want to use their internal data to help inform decision-making. The company uses a game-based approach, turning business problems into easily solvable games that customers can understand and decipher on their own.
Ekar provides a pay-as-you-drive hourly and daily car rental service. Users can search, book, and unlock cars safely through a smartphone app and installed technology in rental cars.
Ekuep is a leading eCommerce site in the Middle East that sells commercial coffee and restaurant equipment to businesses and consumers.
El Toro gives advertisers the ability to target their intended online customer base by onboarding and matching CRM data with realtime IP address location for true one-to-one marketing.
El Yaman Group is a one-stop shop for complete package and label printing solutions, from design to post-press services.
Elcir supplies, decorates, and furnishes upscale hotels, high-end residential units, office towers, and public buildings throughout the world with wood works and interior furniture.
Elenas provides a business-in-a-box solution that empowers millions of entrepreneurial women across Latin America to build their own online store.

Elma Farms provides all-natural, non-GMO snack products. The company started with Mediterranean-inspired snacks such as hummus, quinoa, grape leaves, and olives, but has since expanded its product portfolio to protein ball and dehydrated cheese offerings.
